modules.description: This module enables loading and transforming RDF graphs through operations like parsing from files, IRIs, or strings, resolving namespaces, and modifying RDF XML trees. It centers on the `rdf_data` structure for tracking graphs and global state, while interacting with XML trees (`Rdf.Xml.tree`, `XR.tree`) and document contexts to embed RDF data. Key applications include semantic web data integration, SPARQL-like query execution, and generating structured documents with embedded RDF metadata.
